# Personal Portfolio Website - Nakul Uppal

A fully responsive, animated personal portfolio website showcasing your projects, skills, and contact details. Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript with integrated animations and modern UI elements.

## 🌐 Live Demo

> *(Add your live site link here, e.g., GitHub Pages or Vercel deployment)*

---

## 📁 Project Structure
├── index.html # Main HTML file
├── style.css # Custom styles and animations
├── images/ # Folder containing assets (user images, icons, stack logos, etc.)
├── font/ # Folder for custom fonts (Be Vietnam Pro)


---

## 🚀 Features

- Responsive design with smooth scrolling
- Animated hero section with typing effect (Typed.js)
- Project section with stack icons and hover animations
- Skills section with blob background and hoverable tech logos
- Contact form layout
- Footer with social media icons and anchor links

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3 (custom + animations)
- JavaScript (vanilla)
- Font Awesome Icons
- Typed.js for dynamic text animation

---

## 🧰 Setup Instructions

1. Clone this repository or download the files.
2. Ensure the following folder structure for images and fonts:
   - Place your **profile images** and **icons** inside `images/userAsset/`
   - Place your **project images** in `images/projects/`
   - Place the custom font file in a `font/` directory
3. Open `index.html` in your browser to view the site.

> **Note:** This project uses CDN links for Font Awesome and Typed.js, so ensure an active internet connection to view all features properly.

---

## ✏️ Customization Tips

- ✍️ Change personal info in the `hero-section` and `skills-container`
- 🧠 Replace placeholder project content in the `project-section`
- 📷 Replace all image paths with your own image files in `images/`
- 🎨 Update colors or animations from `style.css` as needed

